{"tid":2216341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"19 歲男被指廣華醫院內藏鎚、萬用刀　事隔近一年被控","createTime":"2020-09-24T14:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T02:45:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b849b8fd19e773a6f8f1c3b6be460b548f6dc4a","tid":2216341,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"網民於去年 10 月 27 日在尖沙咀發起「追究警暴、連繫穆斯林」集會，其後爆發警民衝突。防暴警晚上一度在廣華醫院附近截查，又被指進入醫院範圍「追犯」，拘捕一名男子。該男子涉藏有鎚及萬用刀等物品，事隔 11 個月被控管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產罪，今（24 日）在九龍城裁判法院提堂。案件押至 11 月 12 日再訊，以候法律意見，期間被告獲准以原有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指該男子於去年 10 月 27 日在廣華醫院內，保管或控制一支尖銳的遠足杖、一把鎚子，以及一把萬用刀連鉗，意圖在無合法辯解下使用，或導致他人使用上述物品，摧毀或損壞屬於另一人的財產。<br />\n<br />\n當晚有十數名防暴警察曾進入廣華醫院範圍。據網媒《啱 Channel》直播指，防暴警察曾將示威者帶入醫院範圍搜身，期間又以電筒和胡椒噴劑指嚇市民。直播片段所見，有市民在閘外大罵，又嘗試與警員交涉，表示：「剩係想畀被捕人士知道自己權利。」但警員未有理會，擾攘約 10 分鐘後離去<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%BB%A3%E8%8F%AF%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7%E8%97%8F%E9%8E%9A-%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80-%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%258E%259A-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2588%2580-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%259A%2594%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheNagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=483228fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F19-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E8%258F%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2597%258F%25E9%258E%259A-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2588%2580-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%259A%2594%25E8%25BF%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&h=1d762f85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/19-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%BB%A3%E8%8F%AF%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7%E8%97%8F%E9%8E%9A-%E8%90%AC%E7%94%A8%E5%88%80-%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E8%BF%91%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"45e92c2a348a1e3abd6a4f8575fa6bd7958395ba","tid":2216341,"uid":201359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00463409cef51101087d66a84896259e1fc5975","tid":2216341,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0cc668b60976e30331552687aad0e1b0ec9258","tid":2216341,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"仆街濫捕，濫告<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d4825b9215bfdf2ae8f3221e51443c2dde40bd","tid":2216341,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /